      "absolute_position": 2,
      "lockable": false,
      "has_lesson_plan": false,
      "relative_position": 2,
      "properties": {
        "overview": "**In this lesson, you will:**\n- Review the content from Unit 1: Introduction of Data Science\n- Preview activities in the lessons\n- Analyze data using the CODAP data site\n- Create a plan for teaching Chapter 1 of the Data Science Unit\n\n**Suggested time:** 30 minutes",
        "student_overview": "**In this lesson, you will:**\n- Review the content from Unit 1: Introduction of Data Science\n- Preview activities in the lessons\n- Analyze data using the CODAP data site\n- Create a plan for teaching Chapter 1 of the Data Science Unit\n\n**Suggested time:** 30 minutes"
      },
