      "relative_position": 3,
      "properties": {
        "overview": "**In this lesson, you will:**\n- Review the content of the Data Science with Python lessons\n- Preview activities in the lessons\n- Analyze data using the Python, Pandas, and Matplotlib\n\n**Suggested time:** 45 minutes",
        "student_overview": "**In this lesson, you will:**\n- Review the content of the Data Science with Python lessons\n- Preview activities in the lessons\n- Analyze data using the Python, Pandas, and Matplotlib\n\n**Suggested time:** 45 minutes"
